| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1629 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2011d62f-545e-5292-a81d-6ea3f1947571"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
